Definition: extramarital sex that willfully and maliciously interferes with marriage relations
Example: adultery is often cited as grounds for divorce
Synonyms: adj, all, unfaithful, adulterous, illicit, noun, person, adulterer, criminal_conversation, fornication, extramarital_sex, extramarital, sex, that, willfully, and, maliciously, interferes, with, marriage, relations, is, often, cited, as, grounds, for, divorce
Category: noun.act
